Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.98,end,,0,0,0,,End
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wolf-Goat Cube inside of Sirius could explode at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the city-wide undersea Hug Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Give a hug to those next to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and wish them well!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, today is Hug Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s have one last farewell hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll miss you, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,—Come back frequently!　—There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy, I’m already all grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don’t need a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when have hugs been restricted to age?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you’re a man, you need hugs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want you to leave, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the Wolf-Goat Cube is about to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I’ll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll head back then, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Goat-Wolf Cube is about to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the fragment is somewhere in the western suburban basin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, you ran a red light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s obviously a green light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:02:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what’s my punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your punishment is a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since today is the annual Hug Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we should hug others when we meet them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,can I take any other punishments?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped your stuff, Grandma;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll pick them up for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, child!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll give you a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,no thanks—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for helping our grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has to hug on Hug Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to follow the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Child, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out and accept your hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’d Weslie go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hug Day is so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I better hide in here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate hugging!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Quilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is Hug Day;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone is just way too excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to hide in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don’t get what’s so good about hugging.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s hide in here for the rest of Hug Day together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cube crisis has been averted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie, son,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the undersea Hug Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn’t I get a hug, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck would I hug a goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An Ocean Star fragment has been detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it’s around the western suburban basin’s cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That fragment is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy is so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy discovered an Ocean Star fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I must notify the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This cave is our hideout;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we can’t tell anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we can’t leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you don’t need to tie me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh this? This is just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re hiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re looking for a goodwill ambassador!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Limited position available on a first-come-first-served basis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just knew that as soon as you hear about employment,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you’d lose all self-control!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hire me! Hire me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only someone who agrees to hugging sea ​​urchins
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,can become our goodwill ambassador!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t hug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll get pricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea urchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’d that sea urchin go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have listened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Quilly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you don’t actually hate hugging;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you just don’t want to prick others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not true; I’ve always hated hugging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t leave this cave again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Quilly—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re saying that Wolffy discovered a fragment in…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m at that place right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go find it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Quilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go find the fragment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can help, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you leave…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a way for you to not prick others!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck is the fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re so smart, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, I won’t prick others anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he’s not as smart as King Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ocean Star fragment is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My sponge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun, you two! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fragment is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If Quilly falls like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,he’ll get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you, Quilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll get pricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quilly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,why aren't your spines sharp anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you dropping everything to rescue me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that my spines got dull
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you don’t have to worry about hurting others
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when you hug them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy hasn’t gone too far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a chance at getting back the fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You messed up, Mr. Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you follow me, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since you’re inviting me to a mutton picnic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,don’t blame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is Hug Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll give you a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want another hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can now control the sharpness of my spines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr, Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t realize hugging was so joyful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because hugging is full of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the Ocean Star fragment, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t think you’d hug me as well, Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to hug you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll come back to visit soon, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is truly such a wonderful day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
